data.description: This updated and move-in-ready 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 3-car garage home is conveniently situated just 23 minutes from downtown Fort Worth and in close proximity to the Chisholm Trail Expressway. Located in a great neighborhood within blocks from the community pool, this residence offers an inviting open floor plan with high ceilings and arched doorways. The kitchen has undergone a complete remodel, featuring granite countertops, a new dishwasher, and a stylish trough sink with a new faucet. A floor-to-ceiling Austin stone gas fireplace, flanked by custom built-ins, anchors the family room. Upstairs, a second living space, an additional bedroom, and a full bath provide versatile living options. The formal dining area can easily double as an office or flex space. The primary bedroom includes dual sinks and a spacious walk-in closet. Outside, a covered front porch and patio offer delightful spaces to relax. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this well-appointed home yours!
